WOT,or,Web,of,Trust,promotes,a,safe,browsing,tool,with,a,traffic,light,like,method,of,sharing,what,it,knows,about,a,site,The,trust,rankings,are,determined,by,millions,of,users,in,the,active,WOT,community,The,MyWot,API,provides,access,to,the,reputation,rankings,in,four,categories,trustworthiness,vendor,reliability,privacy,and,child,safety,In,addition,to,the,reputation,MyWot,provides,a,confidence,score,for,how,reliable,the,system,believes,the,score,to,be